claim.claim-text:
1. A medical device, comprising: 
a portion for handling the device; 
a catheter portion comprising inflatable means near a distal end of the catheter portion; 
means for steering the catheter portion; and 
means for viewing through the distal end of the catheter portion.

8. A medical device, comprising: 
a body for handling the device; 
a catheter shaft having inflatable means attached to the shaft near the distal end thereof; 
the body and the catheter shaft containing a plurality of wires for steering the shaft; and 
the body and the catheter shaft containing a tube and an associated port for viewing the distal end through the catheter shaft.
